- Chizat, Peyré, Schmitzer, Vialard, [http://www.ams.org/journals/mcom/0000-000-00/S0025-5718-2018-03303-8/home.html /Scaling Algorithms for Unbalanced Transport Problems/], Mathematics of Computation, 2018 [https://arxiv.org/abs/1607.05816 (link to preprint)].

